<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Conteúdo de fisl12 marcado com a tag "free networks"</title><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12</link><description>Conteúdo de fisl12 marcado com a tag "free networks"</description><item><title>Developer specialized in free network protocols will be at fisl12</title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;The creatress of the new generation of protocols for free networks,&lt;br&gt;B.A.T.M.A.N. (Better Aproach To Mobile Ad-hoc Networks), Corinna "Elektra" Aichele is coming for the first time to Brazil to attend the 3rd Latin-American Free Networks Meeting, which happens alongside fisl12. Elektra colaborated in the deployment of free networks and taught networking in Bangladesh, India and Africa. She is the author of "Mesh: Drahtlose Ad-hoc-Netz" and co-author of the free book "Wireless Networking in the Developing World", worldwide reference in the area of free networks with millions of downloads.&lt;br&gt;The 3rd Latin-American Meeting of Free Networks will happen during July, 1 and 2, togheter with fisl12 and will gather representatives of Uruguay, Argentina, Venezuela, Chile, Colombia, Brazil and other countries. The goal of the meeting is to popularize the idea of free networks, exchange experience between the groups and to attract new users. There will be one day of speeches and another one with workshops with an antenna and a mesh battle (wireless mesh battle). The event will also work to collect signatures for the manifest of Latin America free networks, written in the previous meeting.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who can participate?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Among the groups of free networks are system administrators, community representatives, telecommunications engineers, programmers, enterpreneurs, lawyers and many other individuals interested in help building free networks in their communities. Everyone already registered at fisl12 can participate.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Learn more at &lt;a href="/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/3o-encontro-latino-americano-de-redes-livres?lang=en"&gt;free networks&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 May 2011 16:14:19 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/developer-specialized-in-free-network-protocols-will-be-at-fisl12</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/fisl12/fisl12/noticias/developer-specialized-in-free-network-protocols-will-be-at-fisl12</guid></item></channel></rss>